item.description:
The band's website sums it up nicely:
"Powerful award winning vocals, high energy and musical virtuosity-versatility you need to see to believe. If you’re looking to dance, party, have fun or just sit back and enjoy the show, this band specializes in turning any occasion into an “experience” of a lifetime." If folks want to arrive early for dinner I will make a reservation, please indicate your interest when responding. Thanks.
